fights their demons.

37:56.750 --> 37:58.417
Hmm.

37:58.417 --> 38:00.667
So it's paramount
that you tell me

38:00.667 --> 38:02.792
everything you can remember.

38:02.792 --> 38:04.458
[man] I don't wanna remember.

38:04.458 --> 38:08.000
You want your money back,
you don't wanna ID me.

38:09.250 --> 38:10.542
You gonna fuckin' help me?

38:13.041 --> 38:16.792
Freddy, my partner,
he handled the bags.

38:16.792 --> 38:21.000
Motherfucker probably
called in my warrant, too.

38:21.000 --> 38:23.000
How do I find him?

38:25.125 --> 38:27.291
That diaper bag,

38:27.291 --> 38:28.875
how much was really in there?

38:28.875 --> 38:32.291
Enough.

38:34.125 --> 38:37.875
Enough like a few grand?
Or like a fuckload more?

38:37.875 --> 38:40.792
[sighs]

38:40.792 --> 38:43.166
[movie continues in background]

38:43.166 --> 38:44.792
What's your name?

38:44.792 --> 38:47.041
You ain't a fag, are you?

38:47.041 --> 38:48.125
Married.

38:48.125 --> 38:51.542
Yeah, didn't think so.

38:51.542 --> 38:52.417
Dime-bag.

38:55.792 --> 38:57.500
What?

38:57.500 --> 38:59.208
Dime-bag.

38:59.208 --> 39:02.166
'Cause nobody can pronounce
Duquesne Baker.

39:02.166 --> 39:05.250
You?

39:05.250 --> 39:08.917
People call me...El Trebol.

39:08.917 --> 39:11.875
What are you in for?

39:11.875 --> 39:13.959
Quadruple homicide.

39:13.959 --> 39:17.041
Holy fuck.

39:18.959 --> 39:22.333
El Trebol.
I like you.

39:22.333 --> 39:24.709
Call you E.T. for short.

39:24.709 --> 39:28.333
- [guard] Brendan Donovan.
- Yeah?

39:28.333 --> 39:30.125
You're out.

39:31.709 --> 39:33.667
What?

39:33.667 --> 39:35.750
Let's go.

39:35.750 --> 39:38.417
That's a hell of a lawyer.

39:44.500 --> 39:48.834
- Duquesne. How do you spell it?
- Huh?

39:48.834 --> 39:50.375
Your name.

39:51.750 --> 39:54.083
D-U-Q-U-E-S-N-E.

39:55.000 --> 39:57.041
Let's go.

39:57.041 --> 39:58.041
-  [man]  I can't.
-  [woman]  You can.

39:58.041 --> 40:00.542
You have to.

40:00.542 --> 40:02.583
James, lives depend on this.

40:04.083 --> 40:06.125
[keys clatter]

40:24.625 --> 40:25.750
[groans]

40:27.083 --> 40:30.417
[sighs]

40:30.417 --> 40:33.458
♪ soft dramatic music ♪

40:33.458 --> 40:37.583
♪♪♪

40:45.417 --> 40:49.959
First time I jumped--
for the first waterfall--

40:49.959 --> 40:53.542
I was terrified.

40:53.542 --> 40:56.709
Then I started to wanna do it.

40:56.709 --> 40:59.208
There's something about
being in the movies.

40:59.208 --> 41:03.083
It takes all the fear away.

41:05.417 --> 41:09.041
Things you...wouldn't do
in real life,

41:09.041 --> 41:11.041
you do it for the camera.

41:13.625 --> 41:16.625
I would never take that jump.

41:16.625 --> 41:19.625
But my character,
she wants to.

41:22.458 --> 41:24.959
And since she wants to,
so do I.

41:24.959 --> 41:29.834
♪♪♪

41:45.166 --> 41:49.291
I never said thank you

41:49.291 --> 41:51.709
for helping me.

41:51.709 --> 41:56.625
♪♪♪

42:14.125 --> 42:17.166
♪ music swells ♪

42:17.166 --> 42:22.291
♪♪♪

42:46.583 --> 42:50.250
Oh.

43:06.417 --> 43:09.583
[both breathing heavily]

43:16.083 --> 43:17.875
Oh!

43:22.542 --> 43:23.750
Ahh.

43:23.750 --> 43:27.917
♪♪♪

43:38.291 --> 43:42.208
[phone rings]

43:49.458 --> 43:50.875
Hey, Ter.

43:50.875 --> 43:52.250
I'm at the bar.

43:52.250 --> 43:54.291
[Ray] What's up?

43:54.291 --> 43:55.959
I need to talk. Now.

43:58.458 --> 44:00.792
- It can't wait?
- No.

44:00.792 --> 44:04.625
What I've got to tell you
cannot wait.

44:04.625 --> 44:07.625
♪ tense music ♪

44:07.625 --> 44:11.792
♪♪♪

44:55.291 --> 44:58.417
[phone rings]

45:00.834 --> 45:05.166
- Hello?
- Bunch, it's me. Are you out?

45:05.166 --> 45:05.583
Where's Mick?

45:05.583 --> 45:08.417
Home, I think.

45:10.041 --> 45:11.333
Yeah, I'm fine.

45:11.333 --> 45:13.291
I was worried.

45:13.291 --> 45:14.834
Uh, you got what you need?

45:14.834 --> 45:16.041
I'll talk to you later,
Daryll.

45:16.041 --> 45:19.125
Bunch, just want you to know
I'm here for you, okay?

45:19.125 --> 45:20.166
[phone beeps]

45:36.125 --> 45:38.375
Prisoner's name is?

45:38.375 --> 45:39.333
Duquesne.

45:39.333 --> 45:43.834
D-U-Q-U-E-S-N-E.

45:45.375 --> 45:46.875
Baker.

45:49.041 --> 45:52.166
- He's out.
- Yeah.

45:52.166 --> 45:54.125
[softly] He's out.

45:58.250 --> 46:00.542
Get down. Get the fuck down.

46:00.542 --> 46:02.375
Down.

46:02.375 --> 46:04.500
He sees you, I'm fucked.

46:16.208 --> 46:18.375
Hey, Frank.

46:21.250 --> 46:24.542
So you got what
you asked for, huh?

46:24.542 --> 46:27.000
I did.

46:27.000 --> 46:30.667
I'm gonna need those files
from Nevada. Everything.

46:30.667 --> 46:32.875
Yeah. They're in my trunk.

46:34.875 --> 46:37.625
Had some bad luck with trunks.

46:37.625 --> 46:39.083
[Frank chuckles]

46:44.834 --> 46:46.792
I'm gonna need you to put your
hands behind your back, Mick.

46:46.792 --> 46:49.917
- What the fuck?
- Put your hands

46:49.917 --> 46:51.750
- behind your back.
- What are you doing, Frank?

46:51.750 --> 46:53.375
You have the right
to remain silent.

46:53.375 --> 46:55.250
- This wasn't the deal.
- Anything you say...

46:55.250 --> 46:57.000
- No, this wasn't the deal.
- ...Can and will be used

46:57.000 --> 46:58.875
against you in a court of law.
You have the right

46:58.875 --> 47:00.125
- to an attorney.
- Frank, use your fuckin' head.

47:00.125 --> 47:01.375
I could sing,
I could fuckin' sing.

47:01.375 --> 47:03.041
Sing, you fuck!

47:03.041 --> 47:04.375
- Sing this, fucker!
- [indistinct] asshole--

47:04.375 --> 47:05.500
[gunshot]

47:05.500 --> 47:09.333
♪ dark music ♪

47:09.333 --> 47:11.458
♪♪♪

47:11.458 --> 47:14.375
Hoo. [exhales]

47:14.375 --> 47:15.709
You killed him.

47:15.709 --> 47:17.041
[breathlessly]
Yeah...

47:19.083 --> 47:21.208
He's the head of the FBI.

47:21.208 --> 47:26.125
♪♪♪

47:42.959 --> 47:45.000
In New York, I, uh,

47:45.000 --> 47:49.417
I--I met Bridget's
new boyfriend, Smitty.

47:49.417 --> 47:50.875
Yeah?

47:50.875 --> 47:53.875
Yeah, he's...

47:53.875 --> 47:56.333
he's sick like...

47:56.333 --> 47:57.500
like Abby was.

47:57.500 --> 47:58.166
So?

47:59.375 --> 48:01.834
Ahh.

48:01.834 --> 48:05.875
He introduced me to
this woman called

48:05.875 --> 48:08.875
Emily Chu.

48:08.875 --> 48:12.333
Emily Chu had...

48:12.333 --> 48:14.917
the surgery.

48:14.917 --> 48:16.667
She had the surgery
that Abby needed.

48:16.667 --> 48:18.166
So what?

48:20.959 --> 48:24.542
Well, you were right, Ray.

48:24.542 --> 48:28.417
Emily lived.

48:30.041 --> 48:33.333
She's still fuckin' alive.

48:33.333 --> 48:35.417
♪ somber music ♪

48:35.417 --> 48:36.417
♪♪♪

48:36.417 --> 48:39.083
[whispers] Yeah.

48:39.083 --> 48:44.041
♪♪♪

48:46.208 --> 48:48.083
[sighs]

49:04.500 --> 49:10.083
[sighs]

49:10.083 --> 49:13.083
You can't blame Bridget no more.

49:20.792 --> 49:23.583
I gave Abby the drugs.

49:26.291 --> 49:28.333
What?

49:28.333 --> 49:31.291
When Abby died,

49:31.291 --> 49:34.375
it was me that
gave her the drugs.

49:34.375 --> 49:36.667
The fuck you talking about?

49:36.667 --> 49:40.000
I was in the room...

49:40.000 --> 49:42.250
helping her do it.

49:46.375 --> 49:48.333
It was me.

49:48.333 --> 49:50.583
[exhales sharply]

49:50.583 --> 49:55.709
♪♪♪

50:00.917 --> 50:04.792
♪ dark, heavy chords ♪

50:04.792 --> 50:09.917
♪♪♪

50:12.000 --> 50:15.625
[exhales, breathes hard]

50:20.917 --> 50:23.875
♪ Camper Van Beethoven's
"Pictures of Matchstick Men" ♪

50:23.875 --> 50:27.041
♪♪♪

50:29.500 --> 50:31.875
[exhales]

50:32.834 --> 50:37.917
♪♪♪

50:44.709 --> 50:47.333
♪ When I look up to the sky ♪

50:47.333 --> 50:52.083
♪ I see your eyes,
a funny kind of yellow ♪

50:56.166 --> 50:59.375
♪ Rush home to bed,
I soak my head ♪

50:59.375 --> 51:03.959
♪ I see your face
underneath my pillow ♪

51:07.375 --> 51:11.542
♪ I wake next morning,
tired, still yawning ♪

51:11.542 --> 51:15.625
♪ See your face looking
through my window ♪

51:15.625 --> 51:20.750
♪♪♪

51:26.542 --> 51:30.250
♪ Pictures of matchstick men
and you ♪

51:32.333 --> 51:36.250
♪ Images of matchstick men
and you ♪

51:38.417 --> 51:41.667
♪ All's I ever see
is them and you ♪

51:41.667 --> 51:47.542
♪♪♪
